Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.30,0:02:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You only barely escaped with your life,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.37,0:02:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and now you have taken the reins of our world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.20,0:02:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I am most proud of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.06,0:02:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You are an honor to our family, Asseylum.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.83,0:02:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.60,0:02:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You have grown stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.07,0:02:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Much has happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.84,0:02:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We change as we gain experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.54,0:02:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I pray for your success in battle \Nfrom the red sands of our home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.99,0:03:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You never change at all,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.05,0:03:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.86,0:03:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Trident Base.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.50,0:03:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Captain Magbaredge of the Deucalion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.93,0:03:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Requesting clearance to dock.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.20,0:03:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome, Deucalion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.88,0:03:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You are cleared to dock.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.07,0:03:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Pier 12 is all yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.54,0:03:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Deucalion, acknowledged.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.83,0:03:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Course: Trident Base,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.82,0:03:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,docking bay, pier 12.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.11,0:03:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Begin deceleration.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.40,0:03:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Beginning deceleration.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.86,0:03:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the ship with Martian tech.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.68,0:03:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard they have kids crewing her \Nwho never even entered the reserves.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.29,0:03:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the world coming to?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.45,0:03:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty impressive fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.66,0:03:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess they called in all the forces they had available.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.66,0:03:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a lot riding on the next operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.81,0:04:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Deceleration complete in five seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.30,0:04:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.46,0:04:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.60,0:04:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,One.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.36,0:04:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Engines, all stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.74,0:04:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no velocity relative to pier 12.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.49,0:04:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Power down all systems.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.92,0:04:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we're fully moored, perform maintenance and resupply the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.27,0:04:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Second Lieutenant Kaizuka, are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.36,0:04:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you feeling, Inaho?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.45,0:04:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,More or less all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.60,0:04:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It still hurts a little, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.54,0:04:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have painkillers?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.79,0:04:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel better when I take them,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.53,0:04:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,but it dulls the neural link.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.61,0:04:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.30,0:04:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.53,0:04:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like a perfectly normal eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.03,0:04:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,How fancy is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.98,0:04:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.67,0:05:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a prototype, so the software still has a ways to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.57,0:05:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It still tells me a fair amount.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.06,0:05:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.57,0:05:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.04,0:05:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,49.2 kilograms.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.49,0:05:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you put on weight?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.16,0:05:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,H-How could you tell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.24,0:05:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I used 3D measurement software to calculate your mass
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.85,0:05:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,from the conservation of momentum when you caught that 200-gram pack.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.99,0:05:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I then subtracted the estimated weight of your uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.64,0:05:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not getting fat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.50,0:05:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just muscle mass from training!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.32,0:05:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You know that's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.71,0:05:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see nervousness in the \Nformant analysis of your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.45,0:05:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure that thing's not broken?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.80,0:05:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's working perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.25,0:05:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.07,0:05:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see the same nervousness in her voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.98,0:05:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially during this segment here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.58,0:05:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,As first princess of the Vers empire,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.36,0:05:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Asseylum Vers Allusia...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.33,0:05:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.90,0:05:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If that part is untrue, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.54,0:05:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not the real...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.99,0:05:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That waveform definitely signifies a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.52,0:06:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you been stress eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.59,0:06:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I have not!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.68,0:06:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You're even more nervous now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.99,0:06:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm never talking to you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.97,0:06:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.12,0:06:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing of note.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.23,0:06:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I just figured Inko would \Nbe easy to calibrate against.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.58,0:06:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.33,0:06:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.99,0:06:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess you're not lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.16,0:06:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Slaine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.85,0:06:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Eddelrittuo, will Princess Lemrina \Nbe fine on her own?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.45,0:06:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.18,0:06:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.14,0:06:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.17,0:06:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We found the ship you mentioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.78,0:06:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The Deucalion?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.62,0:07:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like they were secretly repairing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.01,0:07:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I was told it defeated Baron Yacoym and ascended into space.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.25,0:07:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We might be forced to fight them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.01,0:07:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think that would make \NPrincess Asseylum sad?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.60,0:07:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,When will Her Highness awaken?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.11,0:07:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Or will she never...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.77,0:07:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She will.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.78,0:07:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she'll smile again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.14,0:07:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Highness...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.38,0:07:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I leave Asseylum in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.41,0:07:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Her safety is ascertained.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.74,0:07:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Have no fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.12,0:08:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I once lied to him that she had been assassinated,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.96,0:08:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and now I'm lying to him that she's alive and well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.24,0:08:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Slaine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.68,0:08:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think of Vers?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.85,0:08:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no right to harbor an opinion about our sacred motherland.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.92,0:08:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I would hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.45,0:08:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You may speak freely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.56,0:08:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ours is a society where the powerless rabble struggles in dire poverty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.20,0:08:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,By conquering the Earth and acquiring its vast resources,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.04,0:08:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,we could gain wealth and prosperity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.36,0:08:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That said...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.69,0:08:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.40,0:08:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Any wealth thus acquired would inevitably be hoarded by the already powerful,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.79,0:08:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and I have doubts that the commoners' lives would change appreciably.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.09,0:08:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you suggest, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.21,0:08:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Aldnoah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.46,0:08:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who possess the power of Aldnoah receive all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.87,0:08:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the root of all problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.76,0:09:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Well said.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.74,0:09:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We owe much to His Imperial Majesty \Nfor discovering Aldnoah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.88,0:09:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,However, he has been frugal in \Nbestowing this power upon others,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.25,0:09:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and he must be blamed for having created a highly stratified society.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.99,0:09:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we have achieved victory and conquered the Earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.41,0:09:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,we will bring change to the red planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.17,0:09:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Lend me your aid, Slaine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.04,0:09:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I will, Count Saazbaum.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.38,0:09:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,How fares my beloved steed?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.35,0:09:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We've tested the engine and propulsion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.17,0:09:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We can go into battle once the synchronization between the different systems is fully tuned.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.44,0:09:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do that at the base.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.32,0:09:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare to move out, Stygis Squad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.18,0:09:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.50,0:09:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Rise, Tharsis.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.30,0:09:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not activating.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.55,0:10:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The Aldnoah Drive is powered down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.11,0:10:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.05,0:10:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Lemrina.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.78,0:10:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something the matter, Slaine?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.80,0:10:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Why have you deactivated the Tharsis?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.85,0:10:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.40,0:10:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the only one here \Nwho can command Aldnoah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.93,0:10:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That may be so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.28,0:10:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Please reactivate the Aldnoah Drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.57,0:10:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.56,0:10:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.53,0:10:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you ask my sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.25,0:10:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been wondering for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.32,0:10:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you, a Terran, operate the Tharsis?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.24,0:10:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,She must be so happy to know that you still love her in spite of her condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.09,0:11:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We might have the same father,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.28,0:11:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,but because I have a different mother, nobody pays me any heed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.64,0:11:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.56,0:11:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We all admire you, Princess Lemrina.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.02,0:11:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.80,0:11:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.77,0:11:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hardly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.16,0:11:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It is merely my activation factor that you admire.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.46,0:11:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that why you're talking to me right now?{ohhh rekt}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.73,0:11:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Slaine?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.07,0:11:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want me that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.97,0:11:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Aldnoah that important to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.06,0:11:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just a replacement for my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.14,0:11:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.64,0:11:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.86,0:11:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.13,0:11:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I was born on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.93,0:11:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,When my father, a scientist, passed on,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.88,0:11:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost the one protector I had on Mars
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.26,0:12:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and began to serve the Orbital Knights as a servant.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.13,0:12:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot claim to understand your pain, Princess Lemrina.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.18,0:12:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I too have been mistreated \Ndue to the circumstances of my birth,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.22,0:12:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,so I sympathize with that aspect of your hardship.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.38,0:12:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be assured of my heartfelt admiration, Princess Lemrina.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.47,0:12:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Raise your head, Slaine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.96,0:12:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That should give you the ability to activate it yourself, if only once.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.46,0:12:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.96,0:12:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Best of luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.48,0:12:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Now go, Sir Slaine Troyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.71,0:12:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Slaine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.50,0:12:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry it took so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.14,0:13:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.64,0:13:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I am proud to have you as my master.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.49,0:13:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.03,0:13:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.73,0:13:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,All units, move out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.48,0:13:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Destination: Marineros Base!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.64,0:13:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I will have everything that used to be yours.{lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.69,0:13:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So rest easy, my dear sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.04,0:13:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{eyecatch 13:50}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.22,0:13:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We will soon be entering geocentric orbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.01,0:13:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,After aerobraking, we will slingshot around and enter the satellite belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.78,0:13:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Our target: Marineros Base.{can't argue with studio typeset!!}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.06,0:13:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Slaine, standby please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.95,0:14:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.02,0:14:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,As you know, the many rocks that comprise the satellite belt orbit the Earth elliptically.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.32,0:14:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Our Trident Base is on one such rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.10,0:14:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is the orbit of the Mars army's closest base, Marineros.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.96,0:15:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,In seventy-two hours, the two will pass close by each other—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.95,0:15:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,a mere seven kilometers apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.26,0:15:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Close enough to see each other \Nwith the naked eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.00,0:15:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,For that reason, we expect a great battle to erupt between the two bases.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.93,0:15:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,In preparation, we have gathered you all from both space and the surface to form one great army.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.56,0:15:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We also assume the Mars army will be gathering their forces to launch a full-scale assault.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.14,0:15:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Exercise caution while attacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.86,0:15:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I will explain the mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.04,0:15:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}We predict an increase in high-density rocks\Nin the area at the time of the operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.04,0:15:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We've never fought a battle this large in space since the start of the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.98,0:15:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Will we be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.99,0:15:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}As a result, long-range fire \Nwill be thrown off course.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.40,0:15:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.08,0:15:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But surely it's a first for our enemy as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.09,0:15:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Your chances of landing a hit will be low.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.83,0:15:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We shouldn't be so afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.85,0:15:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}But this will hold true for the enemy as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.03,0:15:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Be that as it may, I just can't shake this feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.40,0:15:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Judging from the Martian army's fighting style to date,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.90,0:15:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}they have a tendency to focus on offense over defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.55,0:15:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.75,0:15:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.80,0:15:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}As such, there is a high probability they will mobilize their base's mechanized units
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.85,0:15:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If you showed that meek side of yours more often, \NI'm sure men would like you.{oh fuck off what do you know about men}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.98,0:15:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}and engage us in close-quarter combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.35,0:15:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Five seconds to deceleration.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.85,0:15:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.82,0:15:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.77,0:15:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,One.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.97,0:15:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We're out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.00,0:16:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to multitask.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.86,0:16:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Stygis Platoon, show me what you're made of!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.27,0:16:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Stygis 1, by your command.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.49,0:16:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Stygis 2, by your command.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.17,0:16:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Stygis 3, by your command.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.40,0:16:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Platoon closing in at high speed from lower-Earth orbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.63,0:16:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No response to IFF signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.05,0:16:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,From below?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.38,0:16:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll pass within two kilometers under us
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.94,0:16:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,via a trajectory that will take them straight to the Mars army's Marineros Base.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.28,0:16:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Orders from HQ to intercept!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.08,0:17:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Seven mid-class ships and three small-class units approaching at high speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.09,0:17:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,They intend to launch a surprise attack before the full-scale offensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.62,0:17:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Launch all operational units on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.16,0:17:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare the ship for emergency launch.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.44,0:17:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.13,0:17:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,How's my unit?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.33,0:17:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Repairs are complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.66,0:17:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I hooked you up with a space loadout, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.05,0:17:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.15,0:17:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But you sure about the flashy color?{...lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.13,0:17:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I can repaint it if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.29,0:17:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll keep it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.20,0:17:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a landmark.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.84,0:17:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.92,0:17:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.36,0:17:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ghanaati Platoon, in position.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.68,0:17:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Harroway Platoon, in position.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.32,0:17:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Mustang 11, in position!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.65,0:17:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Mustang 22, in position.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.22,0:17:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Relative velocity to the enemy is three kilometers a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.46,0:17:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Blink and you'll miss them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.59,0:18:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So the attack window's a small one, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.42,0:18:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Stygis 1, commencing attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.19,0:18:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Stygis 2, commencing attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.86,0:18:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Stygis 3, commencing attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.43,0:18:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Here comes the rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.70,0:18:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.70,0:18:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The wind's tricky here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.32,0:18:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,At this distance, neither side can land a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.02,0:18:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, someone did!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.02,0:18:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,At this range?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.74,0:18:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Mustang 00, commencing attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.60,0:18:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Inaho!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.05,0:19:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Compensating for gravity shifts \Ncaused by high-density asteroid clusters.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.89,0:19:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Data updated.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.47,0:19:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Target acquired.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.91,0:19:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.58,0:19:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Next.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.09,0:19:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Next.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.29,0:19:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Stygis Platoon...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.68,0:19:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Inaho!{is that all she says ever}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.08,0:19:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you unhurt, Count?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.48,0:19:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Slaine!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.66,0:19:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I will act as a decoy and draw their fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.22,0:19:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister Harklight, evasive maneuvers!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.31,0:19:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.73,0:19:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's going to hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.17,0:19:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He dodged?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.52,0:20:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What are those movements?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.20,0:20:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's pinpoint accuracy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.98,0:20:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,How can he land any shots in this wind?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.03,0:20:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he just too fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.00,0:20:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.26,0:20:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He can tell where my shots will land.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.69,0:20:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.62,0:20:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is this enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.59,0:20:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.06,0:20:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,An orange unit?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.69,0:20:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.08,0:20:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been looking for you, Bat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.77,0:20:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I guess you've class changed to Seagull now.{>>>>>umineko}{sea cat}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.68,0:20:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the enemy ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.77,0:20:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon to be in effective range.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.62,0:20:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Repelling fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.98,0:21:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Inaho!{SEE}{lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.18,0:21:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Enemy ships have passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.59,0:21:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They're breaking off.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.76,0:21:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep firing until they're out of range!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.69,0:21:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Damage report, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.14,0:21:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The Tharsis.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.74,0:21:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Orbital Knight Count Cruhteo's \Npersonal Cataphract,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.22,0:21:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,later repossessed by Count Saazbaum and assigned to a knight under his command.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.46,0:21:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That pilot being...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.77,0:21:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The orange unit...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.60,0:21:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a training unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.38,0:21:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,A training unit?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.52,0:21:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He pilots them exclusively.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.12,0:21:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.14,0:21:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.54,0:21:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,His name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.63,0:21:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaizuka Inaho.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.61,0:21:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.12,0:22:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Found you...{like moths to the flame}
